  "description": "Aquatic Chain showcase: Fathom at Character 0.18 (deep/dark balance) compresses the boid swarm into a hydrostatic density. Drift at 4 voices adds Brownian-walk ensemble width. Tide in AutoFilter mode at 0.15 Hz opens and closes the spectral window like a breathing gill. Reef at size 0.55 roots the whole texture in a physical space. The engine's slow boid cohesion + the chain's Brownian drift creates a pad that sounds genuinely underwater.",
